During the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], the '''Intergalactic Communications Center''', located on [[Praesitlyn/Legends|Praesitlyn]], played a vital role in communication for the [[Core Worlds/Legends|Core Worlds]]. The Center was located 150 [[Kilometer/Legends|kilometers]] from the center of a major continent.

It was seized by [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Separatist]] [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Pors Tonith/Legends|Pors Tonith]] and his [[Separatist Droid Army/Legends|droid army]]. In a desperate measure of lives and deaths, [[Jedi General/Legends|Jedi Generals]] [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]] and [[Nejaa Halcyon]] were sent to take back the center and the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] Praesitlyn, in which they succeeded.

Its staff consisted of fifty technicians and specialists. [[Reija Momen]] became its chief administrator in [[27 BBY/Legends|27 BBY]]. [[Slith Skael]] was the chief of its communications staff. Prior to the Separatist attack, [[General/Legends|General]] [[Khamar]] and [[Commander/Legends|Commander]] [[Llanmore]] were in charge of maintaining its [[Praesitlyn Defense Force|defenses]].

